title: GameHouse - Jurassic Realm - Match 3 (Requested) [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Jurassic Realm
Explore a lost world in search of dinosaurs in this adventurous 

puzzler. Search for hidden dinosaur images and discover the legendary 

T.Rex in Quest mode. Unlock even more dinosaur images in the 

challenging Arcade mode. Choose your own path from a huge map with a 

variety of travel options. Featuring more than 150 challenging levels, 

19 dinosaurs to discover, and hours of addictive family fun, unearth 

Jurassic Realm today
    *  Unlimited Play
    * Over 150 Unique Levels
    * 19 Dinosaurs to Discover
    * Gorgeous Full Screen Graphics
    * Addictive Gameplay

System Requirements

- Windows 98/ME/2000/XP
- 600MHz or faster Processor
- 128MB RAM
- DirectX 8.0 or better
